high_descs: Turn around and go to the far side of the island.
Pick up a tomato from the island.
Turn left then left again to go to the microwave.
Heat the tomato and pick it up again.
Turn around and go to the sink.
Put the tomato in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a warmed tomato in the sink.

high_descs: Move to the island ahead of the stove
pick up a tomato from the island
move to the microwave ahead of you
heat the tomato in the microwave
move the sink behind and to the right of you
put the tomato in the sink
anns.task_desc: Put a heated tomato in the sink.

high_descs: Walk to the side of the kitchen island with the frying pan.
Grab the red tomato off the island.
Walk to the microwave on your right.
Place the tomato inside the microwave and heat it.
Remove the tomato from the microwave and walk to the kitchen sink.
Place the tomato in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Heat a tomato and place it in the sink.
